<P><HI>But they might have said,</HI> Why <HI>John,</HI>
why must thou Decrease? <HI>Why,</HI> Iohn <HI>might
have said,</HI> Because my Baptism is but w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">th
Water, that He might be made manifest;
but His Baptism is with the Holy Ghost and
