with Water: <HI>But mind, he doth not say,</HI>
Do you so too, <HI>or,</HI> I will baptize you with Wa|ter
also; <HI>No, no: John, said he,</HI> Truly
baptized with Water, but <HI>YE [mind</HI> Ye]
<PB N="23" REF="13">
<HI>YE</HI> shall be baptized with the Holy Ghost not
many dayes hence</P>
<P>This is the Baptism they were to wait for,
and to be by Christ baptized withal, no
Water at all injoyned to it by Christ Jesus,
