to say, <HI>I baptize thee in the Name of the
Father, Son and Holy Ghost:</HI> so that your
Practice in this is grounded of a sandy
Foundation, and will undoubtedly fall.</P>
<P>Prop as hard as you can, and take ye al|together,
ye Water-Baptists of all sorts, and
work never so hard with both Hands, your
<HI>Babel</HI>-Buildings will all fall, and great will
