one for Christ: That <HI>Elias</HI> was already come
[mind] and they have done to him what|ever
they would: And is it not plain to you,
that this was <HI>Iohn</HI> the <HI>Baptist</HI> here spoken of
and intended? And yet, mind, neither <HI>Moses</HI>
nor <HI>Elias</HI> must have a Tabernacle built with
his; but a Cloud came and took them away
[mark] and Christ only left; and a Voice
