<P>But they never cryed out, <HI>Water-Baptism
is the Door;</HI> for Christ Jesus said, <HI>I am the
Door, by</HI> ME [mark, not <HI>Me</HI> and <HI>Water,</HI>
nor <HI>Me</HI> and <HI>Iohn,</HI> but <HI>BY ME] if any
